summoning pouch id list complete
download: http://www.mediafire.com/file/d23tz2decnm/summoning%20ids.txt

-Update-
summoning itemdefinitons complete
download: http://www.mediafire.com/file/nwzgnd2oizl/pouchitemdefinitions.txt - just delete all the pouchs you currently have and add all these in to replace them. all you need to do is make prices they have prices but are spirit wolf prices.

-update- dismissing familiars without summoning interface.
in Commandpackethandler.java
add this in
[code]
}
    	if(cmd[0].equals("dismiss")) {
		player.getActionSender().sendMessage("Familiar sent away");
      				player.Summoning = false;
				player.SummoningItemId = -1;
     		}
[/code]

in commandspackethandler.java
add this in
[code]
}
    	if(cmd[0].equals("::dismiss")) {
		player.getActionSender().sendMessage("Familiar sent away");
      				player.Summoning = false;
				player.SummoningItemId = -1;
     		}
[/code]

no more needing to relog. :D

